dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T11:01:30.000Z","msg":"罷一日個意義係邊到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n話明第二日會番工 <br />\n<br />\n邊個會驚你<br />\n<br />\n咁不如放假先罷喇<br />\n<br />\n唔洗用扣AL<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nPs 支持罷,但要罷就罷到尾<br />\n<br />\n都為果句 罷完第日番工 邊個會俾你逼到跪低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n罷一日只係叫做射波 無限期罷工先叫做武器<br />\n<br />\n等睇咩個個人能力有限 冇左份工唔得<br />\n<br />\nDllm 喇 搞革命都要放假先搞 咁抵你俾支共玩死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T11:04:45.000Z","msg":"節衷做法，實在冇可能叫班港豬偽黃罷咁耐，所以aim 27/28，打工仔普遍得2日病假，甚至請到weekend<br />\n同埋都係想多啲人上街，雖然睇落冇用但而家唔出唔通等國安法過咗先？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T11:20:32.000Z","msg":"節衷?<br />\n唔肯付出就袋住先?<br />\n民主俾一半你節衷住先得唔得呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n罷一日半日 支那佬見你冇料 彩你都ON9喇<br />\n今次就國安過俾人姦完又當冇事<br />\n下次起集中營都只會係同樣下場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我訓覺果陣絕食絕左30幾年呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbce24eb40049ce727e838eb82776abe9f1cd8fe","tid":2034622,"uid":24924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T11:24:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"24ad0962f6424e57d41b4e6ea2383c6618c3979d","tid":2034622,"uid":152584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T11:26:43.000Z","msg":"喺表態  黃店罷工?<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  開花<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63232eec31485bd7b4ece623d2cadefe473a53c9","tid":2034622,"uid":99356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T11:28:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8d8a9972df7dcc970fa9f56b7944d02f6ff33d7b","tid":2034622,"uid":197716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T11:29:24.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"de66e78d0a062b6a952209b96087c58a8e1e8fb6","tid":20346